name: Bismarck (Azur Lane) Lora - ALL OUTFITS
description:
Bismarck (Azur Lane) LoRa

Heil Iron Blood! My friends, the day has finally come where the legendary Bismarck can now docked on your A.I. port. Fellow shikikan, I present to you.... The Bismarck (Azur Lane) LoRa

Suggestions:

[768 x 1024 should give you better results]

LoRa Strength 0.4-1

This Lora is equipped with 8 costumes set:

(4 Official costumes & 4 Fanarts )

use following trigger words to use the costume

1) DEFAULT >>> bismarck, a woman wearing black BMR_uniform holding a sword, medal on left shoulder, BIS_hat, white glove, carrying rigging_machine, turrets_equipped on the rigging_machine

2) Beacon of the iron blood >>> bismarck, a woman sitting on a throne and holding a sword, wearing beacon_of_the_iron_blood outfit, medal on right shoulder, black gloves, cleavage, turrets near the throne

3) Iron Black Elysium >>> Bismarck, a woman in a iron_black_elysium outfit, ribbon_on_chest, holding a note and a pen, black gloves

4) With rigging >>> bismarck, a woman wearing black BMR_uniform holding a sword, medal on left shoulder, BIS_hat, white glove, carrying rigging_machine, turrets_equipped on the rigging_machine

4) Special Outfits >>> Donate 500 yen to me on my Pixiv Fanbox and You will get the triggers for the 4 special outfits 

https://mariegold.fanbox.cc/posts/5585010

The Lora is still being trained to recognize better costume set

Images below are generated on anything_4.5 with 1.0 LoRA strength and Yesmix with 1.0 LoRa strength

Known issues: sometimes, it may not generate the intended costume on certain models

SOMETIMES Z46 WILL APPEAR IN YOUR IMAGE AS EASTER EGGS

I am making different iron bloods LoRa, will release Mainz and Tirpitz. I need your support to keep making LoRa and your support will really help me ^^

Support me for only $5 and you will get Ulrich von Hutten LoRa

https://mariegold.gumroad.com/l/ulrich

Support me on Pixiv fanbox https://mariegold.fanbox.cc/

OTHER RELEASES:

1) Ulrich von Hutten LoRa >>> https://mariegold.gumroad.com/l/ulrich

or https://mariegold.fanbox.cc/posts/5452424

2) Graf Zeppelin >>> https://civitai.com/models/17359/graf-zeppelin-azur-lane-lora

3) Prinz Heinrich >>> https://civitai.com/models/19011/prinz-heinrich-azur-lane

4) Voroshilov >>> https://civitai.com/models/24638
